short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find contacts from a job posting and send them a personalized email in seconds

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Quinton extension instantly finds potential hiring managers for job listings and shows you their contact information for job listings on LinkedIn, Indeed, Ashby, Lever, and other job sites. 

You can also save job listings into Quinton so you can work through them later.
